snippet.title: Stony Road (Ketchapp)
snippet.description:
Play iOS ➡ https://itunes.apple.com/app/stony-road/id1146828763?at=11lGxL&ct=youtube-stonyroad

Play Android ➡ https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ketchapp.stonyroad

Tap to jump over the mysterious stones of a lost underwater city.

Be careful! Don't fall into the water and try not to hit any stone block!

Good luck! God bless you and your TAP!
